{"type":null,"faqId":7119,"title":"手机省电小窍门","answer":"<p>1.不使用手机时，按电源键关闭屏幕；<br />2.缩短屏幕待机时间：进入<strong>主菜单</strong>-&gt;<strong>设置</strong>-&gt;<strong>显示</strong>-&gt;<strong>屏幕超时</strong>，然后选择一个更短的屏幕超时时间；<br />3.降低屏幕亮度：进入<strong>主菜单</strong>-&gt;<strong>设置</strong>-&gt;<strong>显示</strong>-&gt;<strong>亮度</strong>，然后将亮度调的暗一些；<br />4.关闭蓝牙和wifi：进入<strong>主菜单</strong>-&gt;<strong>设置</strong>-&gt;<strong>无线和网络</strong>-&gt;<strong>取消勾选Wi-Fi/蓝牙</strong>；<br />5.关闭后台数据同步：进入<strong>主菜单</strong>-&gt;<strong>设置</strong>-&gt;<strong>帐户与同步</strong>-&gt;<strong>取消勾选背景数据/自动同步</strong>；<br />6.关闭数据业务：进入<strong>主菜单</strong>-&gt;<strong>设置</strong>-&gt;<strong>无线和网络</strong>-&gt;<strong>移动网络</strong>-&gt;<strong>取消勾选已启用数据或者在通知栏中关闭数据开关</strong>；<br />7.关闭GPS：进入<strong>主菜单</strong>-&gt;<strong>设置</strong>-&gt;<strong>位置和安全</strong>-&gt;<strong>取消勾选使用GPS卫星</strong>；<br />8.使用2G sim卡时，勾选<strong>&ldquo;设置</strong>-&gt;<strong>无线和网络</strong>-&gt;<strong>移动网络</strong>-&gt;<strong>仅使用2G网络&rdquo;.</strong></p>","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7259","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1313738397000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":1192,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":33,"times":7,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":4.7,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}